#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn55.51"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn55.51:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.51:0.2"
msgid "6. Sappaññavagga "
msgstr "6. A Wise Person "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn55.51:0.3"
msgid "51. Sagāthakasutta "
msgstr "51. With Verses "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn55.51:1.1"
msgid "“Catūhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako sotāpanno hoti avinipātadhammo niyato sambodhiparāyaṇo. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a noble disciple who has four things is a stream-enterer, not liable to be reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.405, sc2
msgctxt "sn55.51:2.1"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn55.51:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti—"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Buddha … "

msgctxt "sn55.51:2.3"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn55.51:2.4"
msgid "Dhamme … pe … "
msgstr "the teaching … "

msgctxt "sn55.51:2.5"
msgid "saṅghe … pe … "
msgstr "the Saṅgha … "

msgctxt "sn55.51:2.6"
msgid "ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgato hoti akhaṇḍehi … pe … samādhisaṃvattanikehi. "
msgstr "And they have the ethical conduct loved by the noble ones … leading to immersion. "

msgctxt "sn55.51:2.7"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako sotāpanno hoti avinipātadhammo niyato sambodhiparāyaṇo”ti. "
msgstr "A noble disciple who has these four things is a stream-enterer, not liable to be reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.51:2.8"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "sn55.51:2.9"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā: "
msgstr "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn55.51:3.1"
msgid "“Yassa saddhā tathāgate, "
msgstr "“Whoever has faith in the Realized One, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn55.51:3.2"
msgid "acalā suppatiṭṭhitā; "
msgstr "unwavering and well grounded; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn55.51:3.3"
msgid "Sīlañca yassa kalyāṇaṃ, "
msgstr "whose ethical conduct is good, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn55.51:3.4"
msgid "ariyakantaṃ pasaṃsitaṃ. "
msgstr "praised and loved by the noble ones; "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn55.51:4.1"
msgid "Saṅghe pasādo yassatthi, "
msgstr "who has confidence in the Saṅgha, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn55.51:4.2"
msgid "ujubhūtañca dassanaṃ; "
msgstr "and correct view: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn55.51:4.3"
msgid "Adaliddoti taṃ āhu, "
msgstr "they’re said to be prosperous, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn55.51:4.4"
msgid "amoghaṃ tassa jīvitaṃ. "
msgstr "their life is not in vain. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn55.51:5.1"
msgid "Tasmā saddhañca sīlañca, "
msgstr "So let the wise devote themselves "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn55.51:5.2"
msgid "pasādaṃ dhammadassanaṃ; "
msgstr "to faith, ethical behaviour, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn55.51:5.3"
msgid "Anuyuñjetha medhāvī, "
msgstr "confidence, and insight into the teaching, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn55.51:5.4"
msgid "saraṃ buddhānasāsanan”ti. "
msgstr "remembering the instructions of the Buddhas.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.51:5.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
